data.description: Check out this beautiful floor plan with 5 bedrooms(owners suite on main level) 2 1/2 baths in Griffith Park subdivision. Your new beautiful home is in a well established and quiet neighborhood. Granite Countertops and stainless steel  appliances. Main appliances remain (stove, dishwasher). Energy saving appliances(smart). The Spacious/ Functional open floorpan boast ample space, great for family gatherings and entertaining. Extra closet space throughout this home. Community close to  grocery and The Avenue shopping center. Subdivision includes park and swimming pool amenities. Welcome Home!!
